Package com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.management

The com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.management package provides classes for Supervisor management network configuration.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ManagementFactory
    ManagementFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.management package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    Network
    Network class represents configuration for a network used to manage the Supervisor control plane.
    Network.Builder
    Builder class for Network.
    NetworkBacking
    A NetworkBacking enumerates the possible options for uplinking to a Supervisor management network.
    NetworkBacking.Builder
    Builder class for NetworkBacking.
    NetworkBackingEnum
    NetworkBackingEnum enumerates types of network backings supported by the Supervisor for the management network.
    ProxyConfiguration
    The ProxyConfiguration class defines proxy configuration to be used by the Supervisor.
    ProxyConfiguration.Builder
    Builder class for ProxyConfiguration.
    ProxySettingsSource
    The settings can be inherited from the vCenter settings, so the Supervisor settings will be synced.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisors.networks.management package.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NetworkBackingEnum.Values
    Native Java enum representing this enumeration class.
    ProxySettingsSource.Values
    Native Java enum representing this enumeration class.
